Enhanced CTorrent is built from the original CTorrent sources from
SourceForge (http://sourceforge.net/projects/ctorrent/), plus the
dnh2 set of patches from http://www.rahul.net/dholmes/ctorrent.

These are the additional patches that are applied to the source,
also from dholmes:

btfiles.patch: fix for vfat filesystem problems, released 2006-04-25

Fernando (carolo@gmail.com).
